rows.label: bf08250100_0010
rows.name: [ML:undisp ][ML:Dash ][ML:Dash ]

rows.label: bf08250100_0020
rows.name:
Didn't you say you wanted to destroy humanity,
the world, and erase God?

rows.label: bf08250100_0030
rows.name: That's exactly what I said.

rows.label: bf08250100_0040
rows.name: Is that really what you want?

rows.label: bf08250100_0050
rows.name: What...?

rows.label: bf08250100_0060
rows.name: I don't believe that's your true goal.

rows.label: bf08250100_0070
rows.name:
What makes you say that?
After all, we've been...

rows.label: bf08250100_0080
rows.name: I realized it when I fought with you...

rows.label: bf08250100_0090
rows.name: I saw it in your eyes. The sadness.

rows.label: bf08250100_0100
rows.name:
Those are the eyes of someone who just wants 
to disappear, who can't bear to exist anymore.

rows.label: bf08250100_0110
rows.name: [ML:undisp ](gasp)

rows.label: bf08250100_0120
rows.name:
They were just like Homura's
when I first met her...

rows.label: bf08250100_0130
rows.name:
How amusing.
Think whatever you want, it doesn't matter.

rows.label: bf08250100_0140
rows.name: We will carry out our objective.

rows.label: bf08250100_0150
rows.name: We'll erase the God who made us this way,

rows.label: bf08250100_0160
rows.name: and wipe out you humans who live under his protection.

rows.label: bf08250100_0170
rows.name: We are not tools to keep humans alive...

rows.label: bf08250100_0180
rows.name: Well, then, there's only one thing to do.

rows.label: bf08250100_0190
rows.name: As I thought.

rows.label: bf08250100_0200
rows.name: What's that?

rows.label: bf08250100_0210
rows.name:
These creatures have no free will.
They're just autonomous bioweapons

rows.label: bf08250100_0220
rows.name:
programmed for one purpose only:
to destroy everything that isn't them.

rows.label: bf08250100_0230
rows.name: Even with their master gone.

rows.label: bf08250100_0240
rows.name: These guys?

rows.label: bf08250100_0250
rows.name:
They are human sin itself
That's why I...
